# WAHS & Advanced Web Application Penetration Testing – Unified Tools Reference

> ⚠️ **Disclaimer:**  
> Tools listed here are for **educational and lab use only**. Use only in authorized environments.

| Technique / Vulnerability | Representative Tool | Manual / Expert Techniques |
|----------------------------|------------------|---------------------------|
| **Advanced SQL Injection (SQLi)** | SQLMap | Crafting custom payloads, blind SQLi exploitation |
| **Reflected, Stored & DOM XSS** | Burp Suite | Manual payload injection, DOM inspection, script crafting |
| **Cross Site Request Forgery (CSRF) – GET/POST** | Burp Suite | Manual CSRF token analysis, crafting requests |
| **Server-Side Request Forgery (SSRF)** | Burp Suite | Crafting SSRF payloads, redirect analysis |
| **Security Misconfigurations** | Nikto | Manual server header inspection, config file review |
| **Directory Browsing / Bruteforcing** | Gobuster | Manual URL manipulation |
| **CMS Vulnerability Scanning** | WPScan | Manual enumeration, plugin/theme checks |
| **Network Scanning** | Nmap | Manual port/service verification |
| **Auth Bypass** | Hydra | Manual logic testing, session/token manipulation |
| **Web App Enumeration** | DirBuster | Manual endpoint mapping, source code analysis |
| **Dictionary Attack** | John the Ripper | Custom wordlists, manual password testing |
| **IDOR (Insecure Direct Object Reference)** | Burp Suite | Manual parameter tampering and access testing |
| **Broken Access Control** | Burp Suite | Manual role switching, session testing |
| **Local File Inclusion (LFI)** | Burp Suite | Manual payload crafting, file traversal analysis |
| **Remote File Inclusion (RFI)** | Burp Suite | Manual payload crafting, URL manipulation |
| **Arbitrary File Download** | Burp Suite | Manual request manipulation, file enumeration |
| **Arbitrary File Upload** | Burp Suite | File type bypass, MIME manipulation, manual testing |
| **Using Components with Known Vulnerabilities** | Retire.js | Manual dependency checks, CVE research |
| **Command Injection** | Metasploit | Manual payload crafting, OS command testing |
| **Remote Code Execution (RCE)** | Metasploit | Manual code injection, payload testing |
| **File Tampering** | Burp Suite | Manual request modification, checksum verification |
| **Privilege Escalation** | LinPEAS | Manual enumeration, sudo / su checks |
| **Log Poisoning** | Burp Suite | Manual payload injection into logs |
| **Weak SSL Ciphers** | Nmap | Manual SSL/TLS verification |
| **Cookie Modification** | Burp Suite | Manual cookie editing, session tampering |
| **Source Code Analysis** | IDA | Manual logic inspection, reverse engineering |
| **HTTP Header Modification** | Burp Suite | Manual header injection/testing |
| **Session Fixation** | Burp Suite | Manual session token manipulation |
| **Clickjacking** | OWASP ZAP | Manual frame/iframe testing, X-Frame-Options bypass |

---

## ✅ Manual Techniques (Tool-Complementary)
- Custom payload crafting and injection  
- Session/cookie analysis and manipulation  
- Logic flaw exploration, business rule bypass  
- Manual file enumeration on compromised systems  
- Decoding/encoding of URL parameters and other hidden fields  

---

## ✅ Usage Notes
- Start with the representative automated tool for each vulnerability type.  
- Switch to manual testing to confirm findings, explore deeper logic flaws, and perform privilege escalation.  
- Always stay within **legal and authorized environments**.
